{"type": "article", "id": 5859, "title": "Pin 餐具", "description": "", "date": "2015-02-04T07:44:58Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 9, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605234037qAGQFC4atyXsfkdx.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t你想过旅行时将餐具穿在身上吗？最近，来自台湾的设计服务机构 DESIGN YxR 就带来了一系列创新概念的食器 Pin。顾名思义，Pin 系列即是一组形似别针的餐具，设计团队考虑到了用户外出旅行吃饭时对于餐具的需求，既不能够占用太多空间，亦要容易找到与取出。于是，他们决定将餐具“穿”或是“带”在身上，将是极有趣的体验，方便用户拿取。因此，这款设计成别针形状的餐具亦可以扮演服饰配件的角色。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234033eUWY27tyCXpgd5vi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.621875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234035mjH3r19xepJWXAli.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.621875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234035vawu8sA7TUQ0dVbq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.621875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234036miW8j57Vr9DkUS2Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.621875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605234036HrgBdlYeav9fkJx1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.621875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}